snippet.title: Marble It Up! Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Marble It Up! is available on:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/864060/Marble_It_Up/
Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/marble-it-up-switch/

Roll, bounce, and boost your way from skillful start to frame-perfect finish in Marble It Up! - the next generation of marble-rolling platformer. Chase the records of your friends and the world's best players through intricate, beautiful, and mind-bending levels - all while growing your marble collection!

Follow us in any of these places:
Website: https://www.MarbleitUp.com
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/MarbleItUp

Marble It Up! is a collaboration between true independent studios. Launched by Bad Habit Productions and developed by The Engine Company, Alvios, Arcturus Interactive, and Shapes And Lines.
